<hr data-start="166" data-end="169">
<h1 data-section-id="1y209gx" data-start="171" data-end="212"><span role="text">🔥 <strong data-start="176" data-end="212">FULL PROJECT PLAN (STEP BY STEP)</strong></span></h1>
<h2 data-section-id="n9jfhd" data-start="214" data-end="280">🟢 STEP 1: GitHub Account &amp; Repository banana (सबसे पहले ये कर)</h2>
<p data-start="281" data-end="321">👉 Ye pura project GitHub pe submit hoga</p>
<h3 data-section-id="18bi0oz" data-start="323" data-end="344">✔️ Kya karna hai:</h3>
<ol data-start="345" data-end="592">
<li data-section-id="5j9n2t" data-start="345" data-end="377">
<p data-start="348" data-end="377">Google pe ja → <strong data-start="363" data-end="377">github.com</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1irkk87" data-start="378" data-end="411">
<p data-start="381" data-end="411">Sign up kar (college email se)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zezbus" data-start="412" data-end="592">
<p data-start="415" data-end="429">Login ke baad:</p>
<ul data-start="433" data-end="592">
<li data-section-id="ahl408" data-start="433" data-end="469">
<p data-start="435" data-end="469">Top right → ➕ → <strong data-start="451" data-end="469">New repository</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gxz7up" data-start="473" data-end="512">
<p data-start="475" data-end="512">Name likh: <code data-start="486" data-end="512">digital-literacy-project</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pvcxjt" data-start="516" data-end="535">
<p data-start="518" data-end="535">Public select kar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tdt5j0" data-start="539" data-end="569">
<p data-start="541" data-end="569">✅ “Add README file” tick kar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="x0dd3i" data-start="573" data-end="592">
<p data-start="575" data-end="592">Create repository</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="594" data-end="597">
<h2 data-section-id="1as0ty7" data-start="599" data-end="651">🟢 STEP 2: Folder Structure banana (IMPORTANT 🔥)</h2>
<p data-start="653" data-end="684">Apne repo me ye folders banana:</p>
