<hr data-start="126" data-end="129">
<h1 data-section-id="rqxh3" data-start="131" data-end="178"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="136" data-end="178">TASK 1: Infographic (FULL READY GUIDE)</strong></span></h1>
<h2 data-section-id="18txea6" data-start="180" data-end="216">🔥 STEP 1: Canva pe kya karna hai</h2>
<ol data-start="217" data-end="323">
<li data-section-id="1qzbpy2" data-start="217" data-end="238">
<p data-start="220" data-end="238">Google → <strong data-start="229" data-end="238">Canva</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1aui0ul" data-start="239" data-end="266">
<p data-start="242" data-end="266">Search → <strong data-start="251" data-end="266">Infographic</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="162edhx" data-start="267" data-end="323">
<p data-start="270" data-end="323">Koi simple template choose kar (zyada heavy mat lena)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="325" data-end="328">
<h1 data-section-id="oqkt7v" data-start="330" data-end="397"><span role="text">🧠 <strong data-start="335" data-end="397">STEP 2: Infographic me EXACT kya likhna hai (copy this 👇)</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="399" data-end="434">👉 Tu ye headings + points use kar:</p>
<hr data-start="436" data-end="439">
<h2 data-section-id="80yd97" data-start="441" data-end="456"><span role="text">🟣 <strong data-start="447" data-end="456">TITLE</strong></span></h2>
<p data-start="457" data-end="490">👉 <strong data-start="460" data-end="490">Digital Literacy Awareness</strong></p>
<hr data-start="492" data-end="495">
<h2 data-section-id="1h4nr71" data-start="497" data-end="535"><span role="text">🟢 <strong data-start="503" data-end="535">1. What is Digital Literacy?</strong></span></h2>
<ul data-start="536" data-end="649">
<li data-section-id="uhe0nv" data-start="536" data-end="580">
<p data-start="538" data-end="580">Ability to use digital tools effectively</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wctzjz" data-start="581" data-end="612">
<p data-start="583" data-end="612">Understanding online safety</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9pxb6f" data-start="613" data-end="649">
<p data-start="615" data-end="649">Communicating responsibly online</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="651" data-end="654">
<h2 data-section-id="i4y859" data-start="656" data-end="702"><span role="text">🔵 <strong data-start="662" data-end="702">2. Useful Digital Tools for Students</strong></span></h2>
<ul data-start="703" data-end="829">
<li data-section-id="gosfaq" data-start="703" data-end="736">
<p data-start="705" data-end="736">Google Docs – for assignments</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="akx3su" data-start="737" data-end="766">
<p data-start="739" data-end="766">Canva – for presentations</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ocsh43" data-start="767" data-end="792">
<p data-start="769" data-end="792">GitHub – for projects</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gupy3r" data-start="793" data-end="829">
<p data-start="795" data-end="829">Google Meet – for online classes</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="831" data-end="834">
<h2 data-section-id="hbwwwj" data-start="836" data-end="872"><span role="text">🔴 <strong data-start="842" data-end="872">3. Safe Internet Practices</strong></span></h2>
<ul data-start="873" data-end="976">
<li data-section-id="17u0m6s" data-start="873" data-end="897">
<p data-start="875" data-end="897">Use strong passwords</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1haj0ut" data-start="898" data-end="918">
<p data-start="900" data-end="918">Don’t share OTPs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xhbhb5" data-start="919" data-end="945">
<p data-start="921" data-end="945">Avoid suspicious links</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tw2bti" data-start="946" data-end="976">
<p data-start="948" data-end="976">Keep personal data private</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="978" data-end="981">
<h2 data-section-id="142kduu" data-start="983" data-end="1056"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="989" data-end="1056">4. Email Etiquette (optional add kar sakti hai for extra marks)</strong></span></h2>
<ul data-start="1057" data-end="1163">
<li data-section-id="1n4xvr4" data-start="1057" data-end="1083">
<p data-start="1059" data-end="1083">Use clear subject line</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jamnas" data-start="1084" data-end="1108">
<p data-start="1086" data-end="1108">Be polite and formal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8k3ku0" data-start="1109" data-end="1133">
<p data-start="1111" data-end="1133">Avoid slang language</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zny3xn" data-start="1134" data-end="1163">
<p data-start="1136" data-end="1163">End with proper signature</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1165" data-end="1168">
<h1 data-section-id="3usawu" data-start="1170" data-end="1226">🎨 STEP 3: Design kaise kare (marks badhane ke liye🔥)</h1>
<p data-start="1227" data-end="1339">✔️ 3–4 colors use kar<br data-start="1248" data-end="1251">
✔️ icons add kar (Canva me mil jayenge)<br data-start="1290" data-end="1293">
✔️ zyada text mat bhar<br data-start="1315" data-end="1318">
✔️ clean layout rak</p>
<hr data-start="1341" data-end="1344">
<h1 data-section-id="dfvkql" data-start="1346" data-end="1381">📸 STEP 4: Final ka kya karna hai</h1>
<p data-start="1382" data-end="1429">👉 Download / screenshot<br data-start="1406" data-end="1409">
👉 Upload folder me:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1430" data-end="1457"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>task-1-presentation</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1459" data-end="1462">
<h1 data-section-id="hsx7cy" data-start="1464" data-end="1533">✍️ STEP 5: Report ke liye ready paragraph (copy + thoda change kar)</h1>
<p data-start="1535" data-end="1562">👉 Ye likh (150–200 words):</p>
<p data-start="1564" data-end="1583"><strong data-start="1564" data-end="1583">👉 COPY THIS 👇</strong></p>
<blockquote data-start="1585" data-end="2424">
<p data-start="1587" data-end="1995">For Task 1, I created a Digital Literacy Awareness infographic using Canva. The aim of this infographic is to help students understand the importance of digital literacy in today’s world. I included key topics such as the definition of digital literacy, useful digital tools for students, and safe internet practices. I also added some points about email etiquette to make the infographic more informative.</p>
<p data-start="2002" data-end="2300">While designing, I focused on keeping the layout clean and visually appealing by using icons and limited text. Canva provided many templates and design options, which made the process easier. However, choosing the right design and organizing the content in a single page was slightly challenging.</p>
<p data-start="2307" data-end="2424">Overall, this task helped me understand how to present information in a simple and effective way using digital tools.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2426" data-end="2429">
<h1 data-section-id="kw8ove" data-start="2431" data-end="2457">💥 BAS ITNA HI KARNA HAI</h1>
<p data-start="2458" data-end="2533">👉 Canva me paste kar<br data-start="2479" data-end="2482">
👉 design bana<br data-start="2496" data-end="2499">
👉 screenshot le<br data-start="2515" data-end="2518">
👉 upload kar</p>
<hr data-start="2535" data-end="2538">
<p data-start="2540" data-end="2651" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Agar tu bole toh:<br>
