<h1 data-section-id="meo3kg" data-start="77" data-end="145"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="82" data-end="145">Jo maine Task 1 ka content diya tha — usse kaha paste kare?</strong></span></h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1kvvn9b" data-start="147" data-end="198">👉 OPTION 1 (BEST): Microsoft Word / Google Docs</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="12rk0w6" data-start="200" data-end="213">✔️ Steps:</h3>
