translate="no"><p><span>This project is based on the concept of digital literacy, which is an essential skill in today’s modern world. As a student, it is important to understand how to use digital tools effectively, communicate professionally online, and stay safe on the internet.</span></p><p><span>In this project, I have completed five different tasks that helped me explore various aspects of digital literacy. These tasks include creating an infographic, building a digital portfolio, exploring online platforms, learning email etiquette, and understanding cybercrime awareness.</span></p><p><span>The main aim of this project is to improve my digital skills and learn how to use online platforms responsibly and effectively. Through this project, I gained practical knowledge and hands-on experience with different digital tools that will be useful in my academic and professional journey.</span></p></div></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-2 rounded-[24px] shadow-[inset_0px_0px_0px_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07)]"></div></div></div>
