translate="no"><p><span>For Task 2, I created and updated my digital profiles on different platforms such as GitHub, LinkedIn, and Kaggle. These platforms are important for building a professional digital presence and showcasing skills and achievements.</span></p><p><span>On GitHub, I created my profile and added basic details such as my name, branch, and learning goals. It is mainly used for sharing projects and coding work. On LinkedIn, I updated my education details including my degree, college, and expected graduation year. LinkedIn helps in building a professional network and finding job and internship opportunities. I also explored Kaggle, which is useful for learning data science and practising real-world problems.</span></p><p><span>In the next four years, I plan to use these platforms regularly to improve my skills, upload my projects, and connect with professionals. This will help me in building a strong digital portfolio for my future career.</span></p></div></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-2 rounded-[24px] shadow-[inset_0px_0px_0px_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07)]"></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="1360" data-end="1363">
