<hr data-start="326" data-end="329">
<h1 data-section-id="1wxxi9c" data-start="331" data-end="373"><span role="text">🟢 <strong data-start="336" data-end="373">AB KYA KARNA HAI (REAL NEXT STEP)</strong></span></h1>
<h2 data-section-id="wvy8o1" data-start="375" data-end="407"><span role="text">👉 <strong data-start="381" data-end="407">TASK 2 KARNA START KAR</strong></span></h2>
<hr data-start="409" data-end="412">
<h2 data-section-id="1n60mww" data-start="414" data-end="459"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="420" data-end="459">Task 2 – Step by Step (actual work)</strong></span></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="xb7f7z" data-start="461" data-end="497">✔️ STEP 1: LinkedIn account bana</h3>
<ol data-start="498" data-end="631">
<li data-section-id="1hmyh1j" data-start="498" data-end="518">
<p data-start="501" data-end="518">Google → LinkedIn</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="y19bro" data-start="519" data-end="540">
<p data-start="522" data-end="540">Sign up (email se)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="c2s9cr" data-start="541" data-end="631">
<p data-start="544" data-end="549">Fill:</p>
<ul data-start="553" data-end="631">
<li data-section-id="272rt0" data-start="553" data-end="567">
<p data-start="555" data-end="567">College name</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15v6823" data-start="571" data-end="588">
<p data-start="573" data-end="588">Degree (B.Tech)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="c4onva" data-start="592" data-end="631">
<p data-start="594" data-end="631">Year (1st year / expected graduation)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="633" data-end="636">
<h3 data-section-id="1r8bl6g" data-start="638" data-end="674">✔️ STEP 2: GitHub profile update</h3>
<ol data-start="675" data-end="792">
<li data-section-id="huaj77" data-start="675" data-end="693">
<p data-start="678" data-end="693">GitHub open kar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sy0b0s" data-start="694" data-end="710">
<p data-start="697" data-end="710">Profile pe ja</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lja0cb" data-start="711" data-end="792">
<p data-start="714" data-end="792">Bio me likh:<br>
👉 “First year B.Tech student, interested in learning new skills”</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="794" data-end="797">
<h3 data-section-id="1yc7kpr" data-start="799" data-end="839">✔️ STEP 3: Third platform choose kar</h3>
<p data-start="840" data-end="855">👉 Easy option:</p>
<ul data-start="856" data-end="883">
<li data-section-id="2qhncm" data-start="856" data-end="867">
<p data-start="858" data-end="867">Kaggle OR</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="akcs7u" data-start="868" data-end="883">
<p data-start="870" data-end="883">StackOverflow</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="885" data-end="927">👉 Bas account bana (deep kuch nahi karna)</p>
<hr data-start="929" data-end="932">
<h3 data-section-id="1j7iglz" data-start="934" data-end="963">✔️ STEP 4: Screenshots le</h3>
<p data-start="964" data-end="994">👉 Har platform ka screenshot:</p>
<ul data-start="995" data-end="1055">
<li data-section-id="mfqjl1" data-start="995" data-end="1013">
<p data-start="997" data-end="1013">LinkedIn profile</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bp1c86" data-start="1014" data-end="1030">
<p data-start="1016" data-end="1030">GitHub profile</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mygzva" data-start="1031" data-end="1055">
<p data-start="1033" data-end="1055">Kaggle / StackOverflow</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1057" data-end="1060">
<h3 data-section-id="1y2ftsr" data-start="1062" data-end="1087">✔️ STEP 5: Upload kar</h3>
<p data-start="1088" data-end="1106">👉 Folder me daal:</p>
