<p data-start="375" data-end="384">Tera naam</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11iduvk" data-start="385" data-end="399">
<p data-start="387" data-end="399">Profile page</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2sw45j" data-start="400" data-end="433">
<p data-start="402" data-end="433">Education section (B.Tech wala)</p>
