<p data-start="435" data-end="529">👉 ❌ alag-alag section ka screenshot nahi<br data-start="476" data-end="479">
👉 ✅ <strong data-start="484" data-end="529">ek proper full profile view ka screenshot</strong></p>
<hr data-start="531" data-end="534">
