<p data-start="618" data-end="702">👉 ❌ alag README ka screenshot lena zaroori nahi<br data-start="666" data-end="669">
👉 ✅ profile visible hona chahiye</p>
<hr data-start="704" data-end="707">
<h3 data-section-id="12nzge6" data-start="709" data-end="745"><span role="text">✔️ 3. <strong data-start="719" data-end="745">Kaggle / StackOverflow</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="746" data-end="763">👉 Screenshot me:</p>
<ul data-start="764" data-end="791">
<li data-section-id="15upbh8" data-start="764" data-end="791">
<p data-start="766" data-end="791">Tera account/profile page</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="793" data-end="796">
<h1 data-section-id="148qwwq" data-start="798" data-end="817">❌ KYA NAHI KARNA:</h1>
<ul data-start="818" data-end="912">
<li data-section-id="1bbjd3v" data-start="818" data-end="852">
<p data-start="820" data-end="852">Har section ka alag screenshot ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10o3c0j" data-start="853" data-end="885">
<p data-start="855" data-end="885">pura scroll karke 5-6 images ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="onp0nw" data-start="886" data-end="912">
<p data-start="888" data-end="912">kisi aur ka screenshot ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="914" data-end="917">
<h1 data-section-id="1wp9so1" data-start="919" data-end="939"><span role="text">🟢 <strong data-start="924" data-end="939">FINAL RULE:</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="940" data-end="978">👉 <strong data-start="943" data-end="978">1 platform = 1 clear screenshot</strong></p>
<hr data-start="980" data-end="983">
<h1 data-section-id="igasq4" data-start="985" data-end="998">💥 Example:</h1>
<ul data-start="999" data-end="1063">
<li data-section-id="1qq8bd6" data-start="999" data-end="1021">
<p data-start="1001" data-end="1021">LinkedIn → 1 image</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="78ee15" data-start="1022" data-end="1042">
<p data-start="1024" data-end="1042">GitHub → 1 image</p>
</li>
