<hr data-start="51" data-end="54">
<h1 data-section-id="2fm8xl" data-start="56" data-end="111"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="61" data-end="111">LinkedIn me “sab ek screenshot me kaise aaye?”</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="113" data-end="185">👉 Simple answer: <strong data-start="131" data-end="182">sab nahi aayega — aur aana zaroori bhi nahi hai</strong> 👍</p>
<hr data-start="187" data-end="190">
<h1 data-section-id="jujvjf" data-start="192" data-end="234"><span role="text">🟢 <strong data-start="197" data-end="234">Tujhe kya karna hai (correct way)</strong></span></h1>
<h2 data-section-id="7m5ccy" data-start="236" data-end="260">✔️ Option 1 (BEST ✅):</h2>
<p data-start="261" data-end="340">👉 LinkedIn profile open kar<br data-start="289" data-end="292">
👉 Thoda scroll kar jaha ye 3 cheeze dikh jaaye:</p>
<ul data-start="341" data-end="383">
<li data-section-id="1t2yru7" data-start="341" data-end="349">
<p data-start="343" data-end="349">Name</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jnsbca" data-start="350" data-end="369">
<p data-start="352" data-end="369">Profile section</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jg2b4y" data-start="370" data-end="383">
<p data-start="372" data-end="383">Education</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="385" data-end="423">👉 Phir <strong data-start="393" data-end="423">ek normal screenshot le le</strong></p>
<hr data-start="425" data-end="428">
<h2 data-section-id="l51rbj" data-start="430" data-end="485">✔️ Option 2 (agar upar me Education nahi dikh raha):</h2>
<p data-start="486" data-end="516">👉 2 screenshots le sakti hai:</p>
<ol data-start="518" data-end="576">
<li data-section-id="fwyvax" data-start="518" data-end="551">
<p data-start="521" data-end="551"><strong data-start="521" data-end="551">Top profile (name + intro)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vipttm" data-start="552" data-end="576">
<p data-start="555" data-end="576"><strong data-start="555" data-end="576">Education section</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="578" data-end="599">👉 Dono upload kar de</p>
<hr data-start="601" data-end="604">
<h1 data-section-id="ewjj5h" data-start="606" data-end="621">⚠️ IMPORTANT:</h1>
<p data-start="622" data-end="661">👉 Teacher bas ye dekhna chahta hai ki:</p>
<ul data-start="662" data-end="716">
<li data-section-id="1n1h1ro" data-start="662" data-end="685">
<p data-start="664" data-end="685">profile bana hai ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nq5slo" data-start="686" data-end="716">
<p data-start="688" data-end="716">education fill kiya hai ✔️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="718" data-end="775">👉 poora ek hi screenshot me hona <strong data-start="752" data-end="775">compulsory nahi hai</strong></p>
<hr data-start="777" data-end="780">
<h1 data-section-id="1g974ti" data-start="782" data-end="798">💥 FINAL RULE:</h1>
