<hr data-start="135" data-end="138">
<h1 data-section-id="21y7if" data-start="140" data-end="191"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="145" data-end="191">Kaggle Account Kaise Banaye (Step-by-step)</strong></span></h1>
<h2 data-section-id="we629z" data-start="193" data-end="206">✔️ STEP 1:</h2>
<p data-start="207" data-end="264">👉 Google me search kar: <strong data-start="232" data-end="242">Kaggle</strong><br data-start="242" data-end="245">
👉 Website open kar</p>
<hr data-start="266" data-end="269">
<h2 data-section-id="we62ck" data-start="271" data-end="284">✔️ STEP 2:</h2>
<p data-start="285" data-end="307">👉 Click <strong data-start="294" data-end="307">“Sign Up”</strong></p>
<p data-start="309" data-end="324">👉 Best option:</p>
<ul data-start="325" data-end="360">
<li data-section-id="17mzyqy" data-start="325" data-end="360">
<p data-start="327" data-end="360"><strong data-start="327" data-end="350">Sign up with Google</strong> (easy 👍)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="362" data-end="365">
<h2 data-section-id="we62bp" data-start="367" data-end="380">✔️ STEP 3:</h2>
<p data-start="381" data-end="443">👉 Apna Gmail select kar<br data-start="405" data-end="408">
👉 Account automatically ban jayega</p>
<hr data-start="445" data-end="448">
<h2 data-section-id="we6276" data-start="450" data-end="463">✔️ STEP 4:</h2>
<p data-start="464" data-end="484">👉 Profile setup kar</p>
<ol data-start="486" data-end="576">
<li data-section-id="1vvpmzx" data-start="486" data-end="521">
<p data-start="489" data-end="521">Top right → profile icon click</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1t3z3mz" data-start="522" data-end="552">
<p data-start="525" data-end="552"><strong data-start="525" data-end="541">“My Profile”</strong> open kar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ouim31" data-start="553" data-end="576">
<p data-start="556" data-end="576">“Edit Profile” me ja</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="578" data-end="590">👉 Fill kar:</p>
<ul data-start="591" data-end="702">
<li data-section-id="1pl14ro" data-start="591" data-end="611">
<p data-start="593" data-end="611">Name: Ritu Yadav</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1dti6em" data-start="612" data-end="702">
<p data-start="614" data-end="702">Bio (simple likh):<br>
👉 <em data-start="638" data-end="702">“First year B.Tech student interested in learning new skills.”</em></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="704" data-end="707">
<h2 data-section-id="we626b" data-start="709" data-end="722">✔️ STEP 5:</h2>
<p data-start="723" data-end="734">👉 Save kar</p>
<hr data-start="736" data-end="739">
<h1 data-section-id="8w9bsn" data-start="741" data-end="769">📸 STEP 6: Screenshot lena</h1>
<p data-start="771" data-end="806">👉 Screenshot me ye dikhna chahiye:</p>
<ul data-start="807" data-end="832">
<li data-section-id="1t2yru7" data-start="807" data-end="815">
<p data-start="809" data-end="815">Name</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6dfhjk" data-start="816" data-end="832">
<p data-start="818" data-end="832">Profile page</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="834" data-end="863">👉 Bas ek clear screenshot le</p>
<hr data-start="865" data-end="868">
<h1 data-section-id="tadi11" data-start="870" data-end="882">📁 STEP 7:</h1>
<p data-start="883" data-end="897">👉 Upload kar:</p>
