<hr data-start="924" data-end="927">
<h1 data-section-id="ewjj5h" data-start="929" data-end="944">⚠️ IMPORTANT:</h1>
<p data-start="945" data-end="1030">👉 Profile photo lagana optional hai (zaroori nahi)<br data-start="996" data-end="999">
👉 Simple profile bhi chalega</p>
<hr data-start="1032" data-end="1035">
<h1 data-section-id="1446f48" data-start="1037" data-end="1048">💥 FINAL:</h1>
<p data-start="1049" data-end="1095">👉 LinkedIn ✔️<br data-start="1063" data-end="1066">
👉 GitHub ✔️<br data-start="1078" data-end="1081">
👉 Kaggle ✔️</p>
<p data-start="1097" data-end="1132">Tu ab <strong data-start="1103" data-end="1129">Task 2 almost complete</strong> 😎</p>
