<hr data-start="251" data-end="254">
<h1 data-section-id="1qoutee" data-start="256" data-end="299"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="261" data-end="299">Registration number kaha use hoga?</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="300" data-end="308">👉 Sirf:</p>
<ul data-start="309" data-end="364">
<li data-section-id="1d9t8tj" data-start="309" data-end="342">
<p data-start="311" data-end="342"><strong data-start="311" data-end="337">Report (Title page me)</strong> ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ankvxj" data-start="343" data-end="364">
<p data-start="345" data-end="364">README file me ✔️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="366" data-end="416">👉 Profiles (LinkedIn, Kaggle, GitHub) me <strong data-start="408" data-end="416">nahi</strong></p>
<hr data-start="418" data-end="421">
<h1 data-section-id="11o2zr8" data-start="423" data-end="440">💥 Simple rule:</h1>
<p data-start="441" data-end="522">👉 Profiles = Professional → clean naam<br data-start="480" data-end="483">
👉 Report = details → reg no. allowed</p>
