<div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="2295a2db-4589-48d0-8b24-b0e91c596025" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="89">Arey chill 😄 ye normal issue hai — <strong data-start="36" data-end="89">Kaggle ka temporary error hai (Too many requests)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="91" data-end="94">
<h1 data-section-id="uuce0s" data-start="96" data-end="130"><span role="text">🟡 <strong data-start="101" data-end="130">Ye error kyu aa raha hai?</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="131" data-end="241">👉 Tu baar-baar save try kar rahi thi<br data-start="168" data-end="171">
👉 Isliye Kaggle ne thodi der ke liye block kar diya (security reason)</p>
<hr data-start="243" data-end="246">
<h1 data-section-id="2rium4" data-start="248" data-end="287"><span role="text">🟢 <strong data-start="253" data-end="287">Ab kya karna hai (solution 👇)</strong></span></h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1xekitz" data-start="289" data-end="311">✔️ Option 1 (Best):</h2>
<p data-start="312" data-end="379">👉 <strong data-start="315" data-end="340">5–10 minutes wait kar</strong><br>
👉 Fir dobara bio paste karke save kar</p>
<hr data-start="381" data-end="384">
<h2 data-section-id="ap6zxx" data-start="386" data-end="401">✔️ Option 2:</h2>
<p data-start="402" data-end="449">👉 Page refresh kar (Ctrl + R)<br data-start="432" data-end="435">
👉 Fir try kar</p>
<hr data-start="451" data-end="454">
<h2 data-section-id="ap6zv8" data-start="456" data-end="471">✔️ Option 3:</h2>
<p data-start="472" data-end="535">👉 Browser close karke dubara open kar<br data-start="510" data-end="513">
👉 Login → edit → save</p>
<hr data-start="537" data-end="540">
<h2 data-section-id="dx3rrl" data-start="542" data-end="578">✔️ Option 4 (agar fir bhi na ho):</h2>
<p data-start="579" data-end="625">👉 Incognito mode me open kar<br data-start="608" data-end="611">
👉 Fir try kar</p>
<hr data-start="627" data-end="630">
<h1 data-section-id="ewjj5h" data-start="632" data-end="647">⚠️ IMPORTANT:</h1>
<p data-start="648" data-end="722">👉 Bar-bar click mat karna save pe ❌<br data-start="684" data-end="687">
👉 1–2 baar try kar, fir wait kar</p>
<hr data-start="724" data-end="727">
<h1 data-section-id="1lc326i" data-start="729" data-end="760">💥 Shortcut (agar jaldi hai):</h1>
<p data-start="761" data-end="844">👉 Bio blank bhi chalta hai<br data-start="788" data-end="791">
👉 Screenshot me sirf profile dikhe → enough hai ✔️</p>
<hr data-start="846" data-end="849">
<p data-start="851" data-end="926">Tu tension mat le — ye common glitch hai 😄<br data-start="894" data-end="897">
Thoda wait kar → ho jayega 👍</p>
