<hr data-start="69" data-end="72">
<h1 data-section-id="bsmg2f" data-start="74" data-end="105"><span role="text">🟢 <strong data-start="79" data-end="105">Kyu ye photo good hai:</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="107" data-end="272">✔️ Face clearly visible hai<br data-start="134" data-end="137">
✔️ Front-facing hai<br data-start="156" data-end="159">
✔️ Background clean hai (white/neutral)<br data-start="198" data-end="201">
✔️ Outfit professional lag raha (shirt 👍)<br data-start="243" data-end="246">
✔️ Expression decent hai</p>
<hr data-start="274" data-end="277">
<h1 data-section-id="1rj7dlx" data-start="279" data-end="307">🟡 Bas ek choti si dikkat:</h1>
<p data-start="308" data-end="425">👉 Thoda <strong data-start="317" data-end="357">top part crop ho raha hai (head cut)</strong><br data-start="357" data-end="360">
👉 Agar possible ho toh <strong data-start="384" data-end="425">thoda upar space ke saath crop kar le</strong></p>
<hr data-start="427" data-end="430">
<h1 data-section-id="1pfg0yc" data-start="432" data-end="451">🟢 Final verdict:</h1>
<p data-start="452" data-end="511">👉 <strong data-start="455" data-end="511">YES ✅ ye LinkedIn + Kaggle ke liye use kar sakti hai</strong></p>
<hr data-start="513" data-end="516">
<h1 data-section-id="14fvaj8" data-start="518" data-end="560">💥 Pro tip (marks + impression ke liye):</h1>
<p data-start="561" data-end="616">👉 Square crop kar (1:1 ratio)<br data-start="591" data-end="594">
👉 Face center me ho</p>
<hr data-start="618" data-end="621">
<p data-start="623" data-end="701">Bas ye photo upload kar de 😎<br data-start="652" data-end="655">
ab tera profile 🔥 professional lag raha hai</p>
<hr data-start="703" data-end="706">
<p data-start="708" data-end="746" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Ho gaya toh bol:<br>
