<hr data-start="63" data-end="66">
<h1 data-section-id="1vxjj5t" data-start="68" data-end="91"><span role="text">🟢 <strong data-start="73" data-end="91">Seedha answer:</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="92" data-end="132">👉 <strong data-start="95" data-end="132">Haan ✅ ye photo use kar sakti hai</strong></p>
<hr data-start="134" data-end="137">
<h1 data-section-id="1f009g9" data-start="139" data-end="170">🟡 Bas ye chhota sa kaam kar:</h1>
<p data-start="172" data-end="231">👉 Photo ko <strong data-start="184" data-end="215">thoda upar se adjust (crop)</strong> kar<br data-start="219" data-end="222">
👉 Taaki:</p>
<ul data-start="232" data-end="293">
<li data-section-id="1oyk8au" data-start="232" data-end="252">
<p data-start="234" data-end="252">Head cut na ho ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xxouqf" data-start="253" data-end="293">
<p data-start="255" data-end="293">Pura face + thoda upar space aaye ✔️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="295" data-end="298">
<h1 data-section-id="q9vpge" data-start="300" data-end="323">📸 Kaise kare (easy):</h1>
<p data-start="324" data-end="336">👉 Phone me:</p>
<ul data-start="337" data-end="412">
<li data-section-id="th6yoi" data-start="337" data-end="362">
<p data-start="339" data-end="362">Gallery → Edit → Crop</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11hl5s2" data-start="363" data-end="390">
<p data-start="365" data-end="390">Square (1:1) select kar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lf1d1j" data-start="391" data-end="412">
<p data-start="393" data-end="412">Face center me la</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="414" data-end="417">
<h1 data-section-id="11o2zr8" data-start="419" data-end="436">💥 Simple rule:</h1>
<p data-start="437" data-end="484">👉 <strong data-start="440" data-end="484">Face clearly + center me = perfect photo</strong></p>
<hr data-start="486" data-end="489">
<h1 data-section-id="18vf0kv" data-start="491" data-end="502">🟢 Final:</h1>
<p data-start="503" data-end="557">👉 Photo ✔️<br data-start="514" data-end="517">
👉 Crop thoda sa ✔️<br data-start="536" data-end="539">
👉 Upload kar de</p>
