<p data-start="325" data-end="378">👉 LinkedIn khud automatically adjust kar deta hai 👍</p>
<hr data-start="380" data-end="383">
<h2 data-section-id="dmsheh" data-start="385" data-end="425">✔️ OPTION 2 (agar crop karna hi hai):</h2>
<p data-start="426" data-end="445">👉 Crop karte time:</p>
<ul data-start="446" data-end="581">
<li data-section-id="gb08gl" data-start="446" data-end="470">
